  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526580/extras/d0fa14f8b1fab9a9e4babfc56d7c7b21.avif?t=1729087150\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STORY:</strong></h2>Welcome to challenge~<br>I'm glad you chose to try this game finally~<br>Dr. ZEEK attempts to control players'emotions through electronic video games,let your mind be completely destyoyed! <br>You have to challenge and destroy the plan ultimately.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526580/extras/a9d09036d6b98931c1dda934b50d7a71.avif?t=1729087150\" width=256 height=256 /></span><br><br><br>Please keep your hands flexible,enjoy the next challenge.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526580/extras/f48ee3f5efd4cb41bcc65718bf550f11.poster.avif?t=1729087150\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526580/extras/f48ee3f5efd4cb41bcc65718bf550f11.webm?t=1729087150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526580/extras/f48ee3f5efd4cb41bcc65718bf550f11.mp4?t=1729087150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>4 exotic scene with over 48 different levels<br>Design and make the level handcrafted instead of automatically generating the program. Please believe it will be your nightmare.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526580/extras/8e214c6a8a31fd48b84d0b105e12b702.poster.avif?t=1729087150\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526580/extras/8e214c6a8a31fd48b84d0b105e12b702.webm?t=1729087150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526580/extras/8e214c6a8a31fd48b84d0b105e12b702.mp4?t=1729087150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Please pay attention to these bad guys~<br>They'll always show up in ways you can't imagine,stop you from reaching the end.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526580/extras/c975411ffe9f6a5f893c6754175c3846.poster.avif?t=1729087150\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526580/extras/c975411ffe9f6a5f893c6754175c3846.webm?t=1729087150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526580/extras/c975411ffe9f6a5f893c6754175c3846.mp4?t=1729087150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Almost forget,you can sue up to 12 different weapons.<br>I'm sure it's a weapon you've never seen,it's amazing!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple game,drag move character to avoid the trap and enemies</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock more than 4 exotic scene</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>With over 48 handcrafted levels，it took us a while to make it!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>With over 12 unique weapons</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 6+ enemies with unique abilities</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enjoy frustration,over and over</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Surprise reward awaits who completed all levels!</li></ul>",
